            {{pop-over imgSrc="/images/harvest_color_logo.png" hrefSrc="http://www.getharvest.com/platform" popoverContent="Harvest is a beautifully crafted time tracking tool. With the Harvest Platform, add time tracking to your web application before you finish a cup of coffee."}}
            {{pop-over imgSrc="/images/tutsplus.png" hrefSrc="http://tutsplus.com" popoverContent="Tuts+ helps millions of people shape the life they want by learning creative skills with video courses and free tutorials."}}
            {{pop-over imgSrc="/images/partnerbutton.png" linkRoute="partners" popoverContent="Help us make Ember Fest as awesome as possible by partnering with us! We will help promote your brand to highly talented webdevelopers throughout Europe!"}}

